{"tid":323283,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［求助］ 女友諗住比驚喜我 點知比我提前拆穿左","createTime":"2017-07-15T13:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T13:35:08.000Z","uid":39663,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab2046b2983adf50936d2563649cc611c3c974b","tid":323283,"uid":39663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我女友讀中文系<br />\n佢係我地一齊左之後既第一個月寫左篇文送比我<br />\n內容大致上係佢鐘意我既經過同感受<br />\n<br />\n咁我地依家就快一年<br />\n今日行行下街唔覺意開左佢個備忘錄出黎睇<br />\n點知比我見到佢諗住作黎送比我一週年既文draft<br />\n佢知道左之後即刻係咁喊<br />\n仲話勁灰嬲左我<br />\n<br />\n我應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b51a572c7dc59902e45fb9fd138e4721913dc8","tid":323283,"uid":106165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:35:08.000Z","msg":"咁都好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}